{"tid":774904,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（尋人呀！）MTR高踭鞋情緣","createTime":"2018-08-10T16:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T13:36:45.000Z","uid":177630,"like":3,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4fde8c3b8b17a3e0b519fdbd8c3b6bb28d7bb8ef","tid":774904,"uid":177630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"今日我個fd中午搭觀塘線往油麻地方向個時，隻高踭鞋個踭攝左係車卡條隙之間。係好無助，抆極都抆唔到出黎既時候，有個企係佢對面嘅男仔行過黎好型咁講左句：「我幫你呀。」就踎低幫佢用手好大力咁抆個踭出黎。<br />\n<br />\n我個fd多謝完佢之後就冇再同佢講過野啦。不過佢而家好後悔冇把握呢次緣份。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果個位好心嘅男仔記得我個fd，請PM我啦。<br />\n<br />\nPS. 謝絕狗公，所以請當事人PM講返我個fd著咩衫。天佑天下有情人喲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57c286fd9f0150182f136f6777bb80a3c55a0ab","tid":774904,"uid":85427,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"大佬你個fd肥絲大隻咁阻住個門口我點入啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係逼不得已先幫佢抆岀黎 嘩屌臭撚到 我依加仲洗緊手 好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071b1f86585f2b3d79cc6bc1ae949d84328f7077","tid":774904,"uid":177630,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"a57c286fd9f0150182f136f6777bb80a3c55a0ab","tid":774904,"uid":85427,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"大佬你個fd肥絲大隻咁阻住個門口我點入啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係逼不得已先幫佢抆岀黎 嘩屌臭撚到 我依加仲洗緊手 好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"走啦我唔想搞大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19161e5a243bfb25a0261b133760c41122f6afe3","tid":774904,"uid":190540,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T16:59:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50779cdc5cd7048bdd7e58f245b4f1bb9dcb889f","tid":774904,"uid":197135,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T17